<!--
	The Developer, Sarai Hannah Ajai written her HTML codes for the iVoteBallot home page which is responsible for
	creating the structure and content of the web page that users see when they visit the iVoteBallot
	website. The code includes various elements such as headings, paragraphs, images, and links that are
	used to convey information about the iVoteBallot services and allow users to interact with the site
	through hyperlinks. The HTML codes, also includes metadata such as title tags, meta descriptions, and
	meta keywords that provide information about the page's content to search engines and other web services.
	Overall, Sarai Hannah Ajai written HTML codes for the iVoteBallot home page plays a critical role in
	creating a user-friendly and informative website that effectively communicates the benefits of the
	iVoteBallot services to potential users.
