<body>

	<header>
		<%- include('../common/header') %>
	</header>	

	<p id="iVoteBallot_Title">
		<a id="iVoteBallot_Title" href="http://localhost:8080/iVoteBallot">iVoteBallot </a>
	</p>
		
	<p id="iVoteBallot_HowItWorks_Title">How It Works</p>
	<br>
	<hr id="hr_Blue_line_02">
	
	<div id="flex_Container">
		<div id="flex_Container_Row">
			<div id="flex_Container_Column">

				<p id="column_Title_01">
					<img id="iVoteBallot_Image_01" src="../images/free_Unsplash_Images/rupixen-com-Q59HmzK38eQ-unsplash.jpg" />					
					Step 1:
				</p>
				<p id="column_Title_02">
					Check your Eligibility
				</p>
				<div id="first_Column">
					<hr id="hr_Red_line_02">
					<p>
						To be eligible for iVoteBallot, you must have a valid state identification card, such as a valid
						state ID, Military ID, driver's license or real ID driver's license. If you have one, your State's
						Department of Motor Vehicle in collaboration with the your State Voting Commission will send you an 
						official iVoteBallot registration card via the United States Postal Service delivery.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div id="flex_Container_Column">
				<p id="column_Title_01">
					<img id="iVoteBallot_Image_01" src="../images/free_Unsplash_Images/jose-m-w0eMOcfV2MQ-unsplash.jpg" />
					Step 2:
				</p>
				<p id="column_Title_02">
					Register Online
				</p>
				<div id="second_Column">					
					<hr id="hr_Red_line_02">
					<p>
						Once you have receive your iVoteBallot registration card then go to the iVoteBallot.com website and 
						register your iVoteBallot registration card; in order to create your State online election account. 
						This will verify your identity and ensure that you're eligible to vote online. 						
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div id="flex_Container_Column">
				<p id="column_Title_01">
					<img id="iVoteBallot_Image_01" src="../images/free_Unsplash_Images/chad-stembridge-smaioVbs6kY-unsplash.jpg" />					
					Step 3:
				</p>
				<p id="column_Title_02">
					Set Up your Account
				</p>
				<div id="third_Column">
					<hr id="hr_Red_line_02">
					<p>
						You will be prompted to set up your email address, password and enter your debit or credit card
						information; in order to pay a one-time fee of $5 in order to register to vote online.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div id="flex_Container_Column">
				<p id="column_Title_01">
					<img id="iVoteBallot_Image_01" src="../images/free_Unsplash_Images/nordwood-themes-q8U1YgBaRQk-unsplash.jpg" />					
					Step 4:
				</p>
				<p id="column_Title_02">
					Cast your Vote
				</p>
				<div id="fourth_Column">
					<hr id="hr_Red_line_02">
					<p>
						After, you have entered your State's iVoteBallot registration card information and identification
						card numbers, and if they both match your State's Department of Motor Vehicle database details then
						you can officially vote for each of your State and Federal elections from the comfort of your home
						online for an online service fee of $5 for each election.
					</p>

				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<footer>
		<%- include('../common/footer') %>
	</footer>
	
</body>
